係一個空殼 或者只係個有父幹嘅空殼<br />\n一開始可能係好正 但日子耐咗就會悶 會枯燥<br />\n因為佢唔會再發光發亮 只係變成被你綁住嘅寵物<br />\n<br />\n以上情況其實男女調轉都適用<br />\n希望大家都會預到明白呢個道理嘅另一半"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T09:34:25.000Z","msg":"從來無聽過人用&quot;珍惜&quot;去形容目標<br />\n講到目標好易達成咁, 女人諗野係唔同啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e63dbb87692cf4903300090d9623404a0ed3595","tid":910440,"uid":182475,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a6b6a3f7e042dd14a4f2e4c399881791194ddae4","tid":910440,"uid":119405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7264598ed4902a5b49c9c785a1bd1e5ae8f059ea","tid":910440,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0db79e8c8c4210e282f2ca004bf6abe41a9e2e3","tid":910440,"uid":119405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T09:27:44.000Z","msg":"我都係一個有夢想嘅人<br />\n我知道我成日要離開我女朋友<br />\n有冇辦法唔好令佢咁傷心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T09:28:58.000Z","msg":"睇佢識唔識諗 如果識諗 你可以做嘅係唔好將你追夢時嘅失意加落佢身上 佢會好大壓力"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T09:31:52.000Z","msg":"我而家人唔係香港半年佢都已經好唔開心<br />\n日日skype都話好想我返黎<br />\n我遲啲仲想出去讀master/出去做野至少要幾年<br />\n我都唔知可以點..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T09:34:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"569e32b805c93f61919de7691f5d61e95819c86f","tid":910440,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6b6a3f7e042dd14a4f2e4c399881791194ddae4","tid":910440,"uid":119405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7264598ed4902a5b49c9c785a1bd1e5ae8f059ea","tid":910440,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0db79e8c8c4210e282f2ca004bf6abe41a9e2e3","tid":910440,"uid":119405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T09:27:44.000Z","msg":"我都係一個有夢想嘅人<br />\n我知道我成日要離開我女朋友<br />\n有冇辦法唔好令佢咁傷心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T09:28:58.000Z","msg":"睇佢